{"tid":827361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寶馬、戴姆勒、福斯涉嫌串通阻礙環保車發展　遭歐盟正式調查","createTime":"2018-09-19T01:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T02:35:56.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0c56fb90242c25931d3852f4050eaa4c34ec4ca6","tid":827361,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T01:08:16.000Z","msg":"《金融時報》報導，歐盟反壟斷主管機關近日對寶馬、戴姆勒、福斯等3大德國車廠展開正式調查，以釐清業者是否聯手阻礙環保車發展。歐盟競爭事務委員維斯塔格（Margrethe Vestager）表示，這3大車廠涉嫌避開減碳技術競爭，限制消費者選購環保車的權利。<br />\n<br />\n(工商 )<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180918004330-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180918004330-260408&d=9siJFAaRUHZW6EtVwHtQSr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=8ecfaf31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180918004330-260408</a>"},{"pid":"d4c913fbfb7ed7b81424ce42fbd6eda51e6bdcb2","tid":827361,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:35:56.000Z","msg":"歐盟痴左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打完科企打車企"}]}